{"sn11.25:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 11.25 ","sn11.25:0.2":"3. Tatiyavagga ","sn11.25:0.3":"Akkodhasutta ","sn11.25:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn11.25:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn11.25:1.3":"Tatra kho bhagava bhikkhu …pe… bhagava etadavoca: ","sn11.25:1.4":"“bhutapubbam, bhikkhave, sakko devanamindo sudhammayam sabhayam deve tavatimse anunayamano tayam velayam imam gatham abhasi: ","sn11.25:2.1":"‘Ma vo kodho ajjhabhavi, ","sn11.25:2.2":"ma ca kujjhittha kujjhatam; ","sn11.25:2.3":"Akkodho avihimsa ca, ","sn11.25:2.4":"ariyesu ca patipada; ","sn11.25:2.5":"Atha papajanam kodho, ","sn11.25:2.6":"pabbatovabhimaddati’”ti. ","sn11.25:2.7":"Tatiyo vaggo. ","sn11.25:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn11.25:3.1":"Chetva dubbanniya maya, ","sn11.25:3.2":"accayena akodhano; ","sn11.25:3.3":"Desitam buddhasetthena, ","sn11.25:3.4":"idanhi sakkapancakanti. ","sn11.25:3.5":"Sakkasamyuttam samattam. ","sn11.25:3.6":"Sagathavaggo pathamo. ","sn11.25:4.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn11.25:4.1":"Devata devaputto ca, ","sn11.25:4.2":"raja maro ca bhikkhuni; ","sn11.25:4.3":"Brahma brahmana vangiso, ","sn11.25:4.4":"vanayakkhena vasavoti. ","sn11.25:4.5":"Sagathavaggasamyuttapali nitthita. "}